description: Returns information about the configured model algorithm association in a collaboration.

parameters.name: configuredModelAlgorithmAssociationArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the configured model algorithm association that you want to return information about.

parameters.name: collaborationIdentifier
parameters.description: The collaboration ID for the collaboration that contains the configured model algorithm association that you want to return information about.

nested_items.name: createTime
nested_items.description: The time at which the configured model algorithm association was created.

nested_items.name: updateTime
nested_items.description: The most recent time at which the configured model algorithm association was updated.

nested_items.name: configuredModelAlgorithmAssociationArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the configured model algorithm association.

nested_items.name: membershipIdentifier
nested_items.description: The membership ID of the member that created the configured model algorithm association.

nested_items.name: collaborationIdentifier
nested_items.description: The collaboration ID of the collaboration that contains the configured model algorithm association.

nested_items.name: configuredModelAlgorithmArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the configured model algorithm association.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the configured model algorithm association.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: The description of the configured model algorithm association.

nested_items.name: creatorAccountId
nested_items.description: The account ID of the member that created the configured model algorithm association.

nested_items.name: privacyConfiguration
nested_items.description: Information about the privacy configuration for a configured model algorithm association.

nested_items.name: trainedModels
nested_items.description: Specifies who will receive the trained models.

nested_items.name: containerLogs
nested_items.description: The container for the logs of the trained model.

nested_items.name: allowedAccountIds
nested_items.description: A list of account IDs that are allowed to access the logs.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: filterPattern
nested_items.description: A regular expression pattern that is used to parse the logs and return information that matches the pattern.

nested_items.name: containerMetrics
nested_items.description: The container for the metrics of the trained model.

nested_items.name: noiseLevel
nested_items.description: The noise level for the generated metrics.

nested_items.name: trainedModelExports
nested_items.description: Specifies who will receive the trained model export.

nested_items.name: unit
nested_items.description: The unit of measurement for the data size.

nested_items.name: value
nested_items.description: The maximum size of the dataset to export.

nested_items.name: filesToExport
nested_items.description: The files that are exported during the trained model export job.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: trainedModelInferenceJobs
nested_items.description: Specifies who will receive the trained model inference jobs.

nested_items.name: containerLogs
nested_items.description: The logs container for the trained model inference job.

nested_items.name: allowedAccountIds
nested_items.description: A list of account IDs that are allowed to access the logs.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: filterPattern
nested_items.description: A regular expression pattern that is used to parse the logs and return information that matches the pattern.

nested_items.name: maxOutputSize
nested_items.description: The maximum allowed size of the output of the trained model inference job.

nested_items.name: unit
nested_items.description: The measurement unit to use.
